name: Oatmeal Cookies
description:
One of Carol's Cookies original handmade recipe. Crunchy and a healthier snack on every bite. Low in Sodium, Low in Sugar. 

This cookies provides fiber, protein, phytochemicals, heart-healthy monounsaturated and polyunsaturated fat, essential vitamins such as thiamin, folic acid, biotin, pantothenic acid and vitamin E, zinc, selenium, copper, iron, phosphorus, manganese and magnesium. Antioxidants found in oats reduce cholesterol.
